{
  "stem": "268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I have fond memories of my childhood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Physical?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I-- you know, I-- the other night I was thinking about that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I Sometimes laying in bed at night, I think about, gee, what did my father look like?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I don't-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't have a picture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I can't-- and every so often I keep just reminding myself and mentally draw a picture, and you see, remember what my father looked like.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was of medium height, medium weight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He never was overweight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Physically, rather well built.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was bald.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This I remember distinctly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was a muscular man, because of-- I suppose he would develop muscles with the type of work that he did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And fair skin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Blue eyes, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My later brother looked like him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He also was blond and blue-eyed, which later on proved to be an asset.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But yes, my father was pretty well-- yeah, he was average-- average height, average build.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's as much as physical as I can describe him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry, I don't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I-- he was born in the late '90s.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was also born in Czeladz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Seems like 19-- 18-- I'm sorry, 18-- late 19th century. 1895 or 1897, I don't quite recall.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a-- he had a very interesting profession, especially for-- for a member of the Jewish faith.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a coal miner, a Jewish coal miner-- perhaps the only one in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Certainly the only one in that region because I come from a coal mining region.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- he started to work in a coal mine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Siemianowice was also called Laurahuette, which belonged-- which was part of Germany prior to World War I.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then as it became Poland, it changed its name from Laurahuette to Siemianowice.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
